org.apache.flink.runtime.protocols

Interface TaskOperationProtocol

  • All Superinterfaces:
    VersionedProtocol
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TaskManager

    public interface TaskOperationProtocol
extends VersionedProtocol
    The task submission protocol is implemented by the task manager and allows the job manager to submit and cancel tasks, as well as to query the task manager for cached libraries and submit these if necessary.

      • getLibraryCacheProfile

        LibraryCacheProfileResponse getLibraryCacheProfile(LibraryCacheProfileRequest request)
                                            throws IOException
        Queries the task manager about the cache status of the libraries stated in the LibraryCacheProfileRequest object.
        Parameters:
        request - a LibraryCacheProfileRequest containing a list of libraries whose cache status is to be determined
        Returns:
        a LibraryCacheProfileResponse containing the cache status for each library included in the request

        IOException - thrown if an error occurs during this remote procedure call
